### Test Brands API

### Login first to get JWT token
POST http://localhost:5167/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Get all brands (requires authentication)
GET http://localhost:5167/api/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create a new brand (requires authentication)
POST http://localhost:5167/api/brands
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Honda"
}

### Create another brand
